/* READNE */

===== HOW TO RUN =====
mvn package

java -classpath target/classes Main

===== Editor =====

-- FEATURES --

place/move/remove background, foreground and NPC
set walkable tiles
place/remove a teleporter

select/deselect group of tiles (to change background)
add/delete map
undo/redo

new project
save project
open project
load tile
play
quit


-- BONUS --

Activate/Desactivate grid


===== Game Engine =====

-- SHORTCUTS --

Up Arrow : going up
Down Arrow : going down
Left Arrow : going left
Right Arrow : going right

Escape : Pause menu
Enter : interact with NPC



-- FEATURES --

move
interaction
pause menu


-- BONUS --

Scrolling
Debug Mode
